'''阴道上皮内瘤变'''（{{lang-en|'''Vaginal intraepithelial neoplasia, VAIN'''}}），是组织学上的[[阴道|阴道]][[发育不良|发育不良]]变化而形成的一种{{link-en|癌前病变|Premalignant condition}}<ref name="Bolognia">{{cite book |author=Rapini, Ronald P.; Bolognia, Jean L.; Jorizzo, Joseph L. |title=Dermatology: 2-Volume Set |publisher=Mosby |location=St. Louis |year=2007 |pages=1192 |isbn=1-4160-2999-0 |oclc= |doi= |accessdate=}}</ref>。

== 病理学 ==
这种瘤变非常罕见，并在病理学上呈现[[无症状|无症状]]<ref name=Diakomanolis>{{cite journal | last1 = Diakomanolis | first1 = E | last2 = Stefanidis | first2 = K | last3 = Rodolakis | first3 = A | last4 = Haidopoulos | first4 = D | last5 = Sindos | first5 = M | last6 = Chatzipappas | first6 = I | last7 = Michalas | first7 = S | title = Vaginal intraepithelial neoplasia: report of 102 cases. | journal = European journal of gynaecological oncology | volume = 23 | issue = 5 | pages = 457–9 | year = 2002 | pmid = 12440826 }}</ref>。阴道上皮内瘤变可以通过[[帕帕尼科拉乌试验|帕帕尼科拉乌试验]]（{{lang|en|Pap test}}）探测出异常细胞的存在<ref name=Diakomanolis/>。

和[[宫颈上皮内瘤样病变|宫颈上皮内瘤样病变]]一样，VAIN也包括三级阶段，VAIN一级、VAIN二级、VAIN三级<ref name=cancerresearch/>。在VAIN一级中，三分之一的阴道皮肤细胞为异常细胞；VAIN三级中，全部阴道皮肤细胞为异常细胞<ref name=cancerresearch/>。VAIN三级通常被视为[[原位癌|原位癌]]，或者[[阴道癌|阴道癌]]0级<ref name=cancerresearch>Cancer Research UK (2002). [http://www.cancerhelp.org.uk/help/default.asp?page=8822#VAIN The stages of cancer of the vagina] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071007054503/http://www.cancerhelp.org.uk/help/default.asp?page=8822 |date=2007-10-07 }}. CancerHelp UK. Retrieved January 3, 2008.</ref>。

80%的阴道上皮内瘤变病例，都与感染一些类型的[[人乳头瘤病毒|人乳头瘤病毒]]（高危类型）有关<ref>Cancer Research UK (2002). [http://www.cancerhelp.org.uk/help/default.asp?page=8699 Risks and causes of vaginal cancer] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071007054159/http://www.cancerhelp.org.uk/help/default.asp?page=8699 |date=2007-10-07 }}. CancerHelp UK. Retrieved January 3, 2008.</ref>。在性接触之前注射过[[人类乳突病毒疫苗|人类乳突病毒疫苗]]的女性，患阴道上皮内瘤变的概率会减少<ref name=VulvarCA>{{cite web | url = http://www.fda.gov/NewsEvents/Newsroom/PressAnnouncements/2008/ucm116945.htm | title = FDA Approves Expanded Uses for Gardasil to Include Preventing Certain Vulvar and Vaginal Cancers | accessdate = 2010-02-13 | date = 2008-09-12 | archive-date = 2010-03-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100306073734/http://www.fda.gov/NewsEvents/Newsroom/PressAnnouncements/2008/ucm116945.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

一项研究发现阴道上皮内瘤变大多病发于[[阴道|阴道]]的上三分之一处，并呈现为多病灶状<ref name=Dodge>{{cite journal | last1 = Dodge | first1 = JA | last2 = Eltabbakh | first2 = GH | last3 = Mount | first3 = SL | last4 = Walker | first4 = RP | last5 = Morgan | first5 = A | title = Clinical features and risk of recurrence among patients with vaginal intraepithelial neoplasia. | journal = Gynecologic oncology | volume = 83 | issue = 2 | pages = 363–9 | year = 2001 | pmid = 11606098 | doi = 10.1006/gyno.2001.6401 }}</ref>；65%的VAIN患者同时患有[[宫颈上皮内瘤样病变|宫颈上皮内瘤样病变]]，10%的VAIN患者同时患有[[外阴上皮内瘤变|外阴上皮内瘤变]]<ref name=Dodge/>。另外一项研究表明，大多数VAIN患者在单纯治疗后即能进入痊愈期，但是5%的案例恶化为更严重情况<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Sillman | first1 = FH | last2 = Fruchter | first2 = RG | last3 = Chen | first3 = YS | last4 = Camilien | first4 = L | last5 = Sedlis | first5 = A | last6 = McTigue | first6 = E | title = Vaginal intraepithelial neoplasia: risk factors for persistence, recurrence, and invasion and its management. | journal = American journal of obstetrics and gynecology | volume = 176 | issue = 1 Pt 1 | pages = 93–9 | year = 1997 | pmid = 9024096 | doi = 10.1016/S0002-9378(97)80018-X }}</ref>。

